## 六、数据查看

### 6.1 查看所有用户的写作记录

```sql
SELECT
  u.display_name,
  l.name AS level_name,
  tn.content,
  tn.tags,
  tn.created_at
FROM treasure_notes tn
JOIN users u ON tn.user_id = u.id
JOIN levels l ON tn.level_id = l.id
ORDER BY tn.created_at DESC;
```

### 6.2 查看特定用户的写作

```sql
SELECT
  l.name AS level_name,
  tn.content,
  tn.tags,
  tn.created_at
FROM treasure_notes tn
JOIN levels l ON tn.level_id = l.id
WHERE tn.user_id = '用户的uuid'
ORDER BY tn.created_at DESC;
```

### 6.3 查看特定关卡的所有写作

```sql
SELECT
  u.display_name,
  tn.content,
  tn.tags,
  tn.created_at
FROM treasure_notes tn
JOIN users u ON tn.user_id = u.id
WHERE tn.level_id = '关卡ID'
ORDER BY tn.created_at DESC;
```

### 6.4 查看用户练习时长统计

```sql
SELECT
  u.display_name,
  ROUND(SUM(up.total_sec) / 60) AS total_minutes,
  COUNT(DISTINCT up.level_id) AS levels_explored
FROM user_progress up
JOIN users u ON up.user_id = u.id
GROUP BY u.id, u.display_name
ORDER BY total_minutes DESC;
```

### 6.5 查看单个用户的练习详情

```sql
SELECT
  l.name AS level_name,
  ROUND(up.total_sec / 60) AS minutes,
  up.last_pos,
  up.updated_at
FROM user_progress up
JOIN levels l ON up.level_id = l.id
WHERE up.user_id = '用户的uuid'
ORDER BY up.updated_at DESC;
```

